AI Interview Coach & Planner

An intelligent AI-powered interview preparation platform that analyzes your resume (PDF) + job description and generates a personalized interview preparation report using Google Gemini AI.

 Features
 Upload Resume (PDF)
 Provide Job Description
AI-powered analysis using Gemini API
 Generates:
Skill Gap Analysis
Preparation Plan
Interview Readiness Report
Behavioral Questions
Secure Authentication using JWT
Personalized, structured output for interview success
AI Integration (Google Gemini)

This project uses Google Gemini API to intelligently analyze user input.

 What AI does:
Extracts skills from resume
Matches with job description
Identifies missing skills
Generates preparation roadmap
Creates behavioral interview questions
Provides interview readiness score
⚙️ AI Workflow
 Resume + Job Description received
 Text extraction & preprocessing
 Prompt sent to Gemini API
 AI generates structured response
 Data mapped into schemas
 Final report returned to user


Use Cases
Placement preparation
Job switch planning
Resume optimization
Targeted interview practice




